    "description": "21-day aged sirloin steak takes centre stage in this elegant, mouth-watering dish. Using simple techniques, you'll create an array of textures to compliment your juicy, rich steak like velvety parsnip pur\u00e9e and crisp potato r\u00f6stis, all finished with garlicky spinach and a redcurrant jus.",
